              Information Sharing
              %br/
              When you submit information to BeMyMBA, it is collected, processed and maintained solely by us or by third party Agents who are bound by confidentiality obligations. We may allow our business partners to collect information about Users that is not extremely sensitive Information. If you would like to opt out from the onward transfer of your information to our non-agent partners, you may send us an email at info@BeMyMBA.com. Include the word ”privacy” in the subject line of the email and all your registration information in the body of the email.
